name: iVote
description: iVote is a Ruby on Rails app that allows users to register to vote by text message. After texting 'Register' to a shortcode (which interfaces the application through the use of CDYNE's SMS API), users are instructed to provide mailing address information to register to vote. News articles on the application: http://kxan.com/2015/08/05/travis-county-waiting-for-guidance-on-voter-id-law-appeal/, http://www.govtech.com/dc/articles/Travis-County-Texas-Entices-Millennials-to-Register-to-Vote-via-Text.html, http://www.austinchronicle.com/news/2015-08-14/travis-voter-registrar-tests-text-request/, News Article
